{
  "uid": "online-game-llm",
  "title": "Online Galaxy War — LLM usage & GPU",
  "tags": ["online-game", "llm", "gpu"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 4,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "stat", "title": "LLM in-flight",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(litellm_in_flight_requests)" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "stat", "title": "Requests/s (5m) — TODOS los servicios",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_proxy_total_requests_metric_total[5m]))" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3, "type": "stat", "title": "GPU VRAM asignada (total, GPU compartida)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(hami_gpu_memory_allocated_bytes)" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4, "type": "stat", "title": "Fallbacks/s (5m) — TODOS los servicios",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_deployment_successful_fallbacks_total[5m]))" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Requests/s por backend — TODOS los servicios (proxy)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (requested_model) (rate(litellm_proxy_total_requests_metric_total[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{requested_model}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Tokens de salida/s por modelo (backend real)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{model}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7, "type": "table", "title": "Tokens por usuario (24h) — salida",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "format": "table", "instant": true, "expr": "sort_desc(sum by (end_user) (increase(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\"}[24h])))", "legendFormat": "{{end_user}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8, "type": "table", "title": "Spend USD por usuario × backend (24h) — monetización",
      "description": "litellm_spend_metric: costo real en USD por end_user y modelo. Está CASI EN CERO A PROPÓSITO: la IA del jugador (asistente + autopilot + agente) corre en la GPU LOCAL (qwen2.5) que cuesta $0; solo el fallback a la NUBE (google/gemma-4-31b-it) paga centavos, casi siempre por las NPC. O sea: 0 ≈ 'estás gastando casi nada', no 'está roto'. El total histórico se ve en el stat de al lado.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 9, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "format": "table", "instant": true, "expr": "sort_desc(sum by (end_user, model) (increase(litellm_spend_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\"}[24h])))", "legendFormat": "{{end_user}} / {{model}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30, "type": "stat", "title": "Spend USD total (histórico)",
      "description": "sum(litellm_spend_metric): lo gastado en la nube desde siempre por online-game. Corre en GPU local → esto crece lentísimo (solo el fallback a la nube paga).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD", "decimals": 4 }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 3, "x": 21, "y": 12 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(litellm_spend_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\"})" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9, "type": "timeseries", "title": "GPU — VRAM asignada por placa (HAMI)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "hami_gpu_memory_allocated_bytes", "legendFormat": "{{device_type}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10, "type": "timeseries", "title": "GPU — cores asignados por placa (HAMI, %)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100 }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 20 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "hami_gpu_core_allocated_ratio", "legendFormat": "{{device_type}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11, "type": "table", "title": "Tokens por usuario × fuente — GPU vs nube (24h)",
      "description": "source=gpu si el modelo servido es local (qwen → GPU); nube = OpenRouter (fallback/free/pago).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "format": "table", "instant": true, "expr": "sort_desc(sum by (end_user, source) (label_replace(label_replace(increase(litellm_total_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\"}[24h]), \"source\", \"nube\", \"model\", \".+\"), \"source\", \"gpu\", \"model\", \"qwen.*\")))" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Tokens de salida/s GPU vs nube (online-game)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 28 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\",model=~\"qwen.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "GPU (local)" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:.*\",model!~\"qwen.*\",model!=\"\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "nube (OpenRouter)" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Carga por instancia Ollama (P4 = ollama-a / M4000 = ollama-b)",
      "description": "VRAM asignada por HAMI a cada pod Ollama (exported_pod) → qué instancia/placa está cargada.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 36 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "hami_vgpu_memory_allocated_bytes{exported_pod=~\"ollama.*\"}", "legendFormat": "{{exported_pod}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Tokens de salida/s por TIPO de IA (asistente/autopilot/agente/NPC)",
      "description": "Separa por el prefijo del end_user. asistente = online-game:player:* (el chat que le habla el jugador) · autopilot = online-game:autopilot:* (el cerebro SDD 81 que elige skill) · agente = online-game:agent:* (SDD 83, ejecuta acciones) · NPC = online-game:npc:* (bots). Así ves QUÉ IA consume tokens, no solo 'usuarios vs bots'.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 44 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:player:.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "asistente (chat)" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:autopilot:.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "autopilot (elige skill)" },
        { "refId": "C", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:agent:.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "agente (ejecuta)" },
        { "refId": "D", "expr": "sum(rate(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:npc:.*\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "NPC (bots)" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 15, "type": "table", "title": "Consultas por TIPO de IA y JUGADOR (24h)",
      "description": "Tokens de salida (24h) por end_user = tipo:jugador. Ves p.ej. autopilot:villadalmine (su IA jugando sola) vs player:villadalmine (su chat con el asistente) — el grado por-jugador que faltaba.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 44 },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "format": "table", "instant": true, "expr": "sort_desc(sum by (end_user) (increase(litellm_output_tokens_metric_total{end_user=~\"online-game:(player|autopilot|agent|npc):.*\"}[24h])))", "legendFormat": "{{end_user}}" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20, "type": "text", "title": "🔎 ¿La API pega a MI GPU? (métricas del propio juego)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 52 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "Los paneles de arriba son la vista de **LiteLLM/HAMI** (el proxy/GPU). Los de ABAJO salen del **`/metrics` del propio juego** (`game_llm_*`) → prueban que la API del juego llegó a la GPU y cuentan tokens sin depender del proxy. **route** = `gpu` (local) / `cloud` / `byok`. Si `game_llm_route_total{route=\"gpu\",status=\"ok\"}` sube y el heartbeat está en verde, tu GPU está respondiendo de verdad." }
    },
    {
      "id": 21, "type": "stat", "title": "GPU viva — seg. desde la última respuesta OK (juego)",
      "description": "time() - game_llm_last_ok_timestamp{route=gpu}. Verde = tu GPU respondió hace poco; rojo = hace rato que no (¿caída a nube/reglas?).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 300 }, { "color": "red", "value": 900 } ] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 55 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "time() - max(game_llm_last_ok_timestamp{route=\"gpu\"})" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 22, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Llamadas del JUEGO al LLM por ruta (ok/error, rate 5m)",
      "description": "game_llm_route_total: llamadas que hizo la API del juego, separadas por backend y resultado. route=gpu con ok>0 = tu GPU atiende.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 9, "x": 6, "y": 55 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (route, status) (rate(game_llm_route_total[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{route}} / {{status}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 23, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Tokens que el JUEGO ve por ruta (rate 5m)",
      "description": "game_llm_tokens_total del campo `usage` de la respuesta (prompt/completion), por backend. Sube en route=gpu = la GPU genera tokens de verdad.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 9, "x": 15, "y": 55 },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (route, type) (rate(game_llm_tokens_total[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{route}} / {{type}}" } ]
    }
  ]
}
